TITLEMedici: Masters of FlorenceSTARRING Richard Madden, Stuart Martin, Annabel Scholey, Dustin HoffmanGENREHistorical fictionRelease DateDecember 9, 2016 The show is based on the prominent Medici family, who at one point in time owned the largest bank in Europe. Set in 15th century Florence, Cosimo the son of Giovanni has become the patriarch of the family and head of the bank, after his father&rsquo;s sudden death. The show seeks to expose (partly fictitiously) how the Medici family became the most politically and financially influential family in Europe. It weaves between the past and the future to unravel the relationships between father and sons. This show is a must watch for any history buff. Star Rating: 4/5